{"tid":2265543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老蘭唔敢告，太子站兩個人就犯限聚令","createTime":"2020-10-31T13:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T14:26:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec4a5b123d09cc0fe781e7674e6a13de0ff9ffe","tid":2265543,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:57:54.000Z","msg":"Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n5 m  &middot;<br />\n【警發限聚令告票的標準】<br />\n<br />\n今晚是萬聖節，疫情之下，政府的 4 人限聚令續生效，不少市民照常出外慶祝。中環蘭桂坊更是人山人海。大批警員實施人流管制，但未有警告人群違反限聚令，只呼籲市民向前行，「上返行人路」。<br />\n<br />\n今日是「831 太子站襲擊事件」發生 14 個月，有市民由傍晚起陸續到場獻花，但人數不多。晚上 8 時許，附近大廈間傳來「死黑警」、「黑警死全家」等口號，地面有人和應，大批警員隨後突然推進，到聯合廣場後 B2 出口一帶，舉藍旗驅散市民。<br />\n<br />\n現場有多組市民分別被截查，期間一名戴豬嘴男士曾與警員爭執，不滿警方突然清場，他與同行的伍女士未幾被多名警員帶到後巷，被票控違反限聚令。伍女士事後批評警方無理，她指同行只有二人，「邊度搵四個人呢？打橫來講。」她表明會抗辯，不會交罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3604073413011586/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3604073413011586%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak7QTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=72a7ba6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3604073413011586/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/123002714_3604073419678252_2133606124005243088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=JMUIOjgGAe0AX_59GIG&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-2.xx&amp;oh=7751e67fed1a5ba905c3d15d1d62fbde&amp;oe=5FC2C68C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F123002714_3604073419678252_2133606124005243088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DJMUIOjgGAe0AX_59GIG%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-2.xx%26oh%3D7751e67fed1a5ba905c3d15d1d62fbde%26oe%3D5FC2C68C&h=09ddc719&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83486078cb5f907fa3915432f5567b5e1ea666f4","tid":2265543,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20